 Muse CC Web Design with Scroll Effects

 This course reviews how to build a one-page website using
 Scroll Effects inside of Muse CC. We cover everything from
 planning the site, creating a navigation system, and building
 the different sections of the site. Once you have everything
 in place, the course continues, to demonstrate how you can
 use the Scroll Effects panel to create visually compelling
 transitions between the sections. The site that's built in
 the course is based off a template provided to us by our
 friends, MuseGrid.com.
